ent-ClothingOuterSuitBomb = сапёрный костюм
    .desc = A heavy suit designed to withstand the pressure generated by a bomb and any fragments the bomb may produce.
ent-ClothingOuterSuitJanitorBomb = костюм уборщика-сапёра
    .desc = Heavy body armor designed to withstand explosions formed from reactions between chemicals.
ent-ClothingOuterSuitFire = пожарный костюм
    .desc = A suit that helps protect against hazardous temperatures.
ent-ClothingOuterSuitAtmosFire = атмос-пожарный костюм
    .desc = An expensive firesuit that protects against even the most deadly of station fires. Designed to protect even if the wearer is set aflame.
ent-ClothingOuterSuitRad = противорадиационный костюм
    .desc = A suit that protects against radiation. The label reads, 'Made with lead. Please do not consume insulation.'
ent-ClothingOuterSuitSpaceNinja = костюм космического ниндзя
    .desc = This black technologically advanced, cybernetically-enhanced suit provides many abilities like invisibility or teleportation.
ent-ClothingOuterSuitChicken = костюм цыплёнка
    .desc = Bok bok bok!
ent-ClothingOuterSuitShrineMaiden = наряд служительницы храма
    .desc = Makes you want to go deal with some troublesome youkai.
ent-ClothingOuterSuitWitchRobes = одеяние ведьмы
    .desc = Magic is all about the spell power, ZE!
ent-ClothingOuterSuitMonkey = костюм обезьяны
    .desc = A suit that looks like a primate.
ent-ClothingOuterSuitIan = костюм Иана
    .desc = Who's a good boy?
ent-ClothingOuterSuitCarp = костюм космического карпа
    .desc = A special suit that makes you look just like a space carp, if your eyesight is bad.
ent-ClothingOuterHardsuitCarp = { ent-ClothingOuterSuitCarp }
    .suffix = Hardsuit, DO NOT MAP
    .desc = { ent-ClothingOuterSuitCarp.desc }
